description: Contains the classes for interaction with TruCharge

Dehydrator helps you combine ORMs like Entity Framework with REST service frameworks like WebAPI.
By stripping navigational references in your entities down to only their IDs their serialized representation no longer contains redundant or cyclic data. When new or modified deserialized data needs to be persisted Dehydrator takes care of resolving the reference IDs again.
Install this package in your data model. Install Dehydrator.EntityFramework and EntityFramework.WebApi in your controller if you use Entity Framework and WebAPI.
summary: Dehydrates references in Entity objects down to nothing but their ID for better serializability

            The quite captivating fact about the API is, its UI less and independent calls can be made. 
            It also provides useful features to manipulate documents and signatures.
    
            Signature Types:
            - Text Signature
            - Image Signature
            - Digital Signature
            
            API provides a useful feature to manipulate list of signature. Like accessing, browsing stored signatures.
            
            For more details on the library, please visit GroupDocs website at:
            http://groupdocs.com/dot-net/electronic-signature-library
            
            Note: The library comes up with some limitations in the evaluation mode. In order to test full features of GroupDocs.Signature for .NET library, please request a free 30-day temporary license.
summary: GroupDocs.Signature for .NET allows developers to write applications with ability to significantly sign electronic docs.

“PDF.NET框架”全称是“PWMIS数据开发框架”（有关名字的由来请看官网http://www.pwmis.com/sqlmap/ 介绍），它直接基于 ADO.NET，没有使用反射，没有过度封装，力求做速度最快、使用最简单、适应场景最广泛的的数据开发框架。框架自2006年推出第一版，到现在为止已经在实际项目中使用了9年了，框架中的每一行代码都是实际项目的总结。为了让更多的朋友使用本框架，自Ver3.0 开源之后，后续各个版本陆续保持开源，但是，之前的开源，都仅限于核心类库和一些Demo程序，而框架的支持工具仅面向会员用户开源，今天，我宣布PDF.NET SOD框架完全开源！
